Package DecaTeamOrganizer

Class Member

java.lang.Object
DecaTeamOrganizer.Member
public class Member
extends java.lang.Object
The Member class containing instance fields and methods for each Member that will be added in the DECA team organizer.
Author:
Hugh Jiang
